summary: And here’s my piece for the @laytonzine! It was such a wonderful opportunity to work on this zine with the others artists (who...
caption: And here’s my piece for the @laytonzine! It was such a wonderful opportunity to work on this zine with the others artists (who are great please check what they all do) so I can’t thank the staff enough for being so nice and competent; Professor Layton means so much to me since my childhood that being able to pay it tribute like this is a pleasure, especially the Pandora’s box game who was my very first Layton’s game. I hope you will all enjoy our works for this zine~
